---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About — ZeroClue"
  description="Software architect. Building Kern, CoolMinds, and MFTPlus."
>
  <style>
    .about { margin: 2.5rem 0; }
    .about h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    }
    .about p { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .ventures { margin-top: 2rem; }
    .ventures h2 {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }
    .ventures ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
    .ventures li { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .ventures .desc { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem; }
  </style>
  <div class="about">
    <h1>Armin Marxer</h1>
    <p>Software solutions architect and engineer. Auto-didact. I build things — currently three of them.</p>
    <p>This is where I write. No theme, no schedule. Technical deep-dives, founder notes, opinions I haven't been talked out of yet.</p>
    <div class="ventures">
      <h2>Ventures</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://kern.web.za">Kern</a>
          <span class="desc"> — AI-assisted web design for South African businesses</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://coolminds.co.za">CoolMinds</a>
          <span class="desc"> — Software engineering for founders and CTOs</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://mftplus.co.za">MFTPlus</a>
          <span class="desc"> — Managed file transfer infrastructure</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
